        output="# Matching 模块实现\n\n## 职责\n\n负责推荐卡片生成、滑动操作处理
、双向匹配判定与通知。\n\n## 流程图\n\n### 推荐卡片\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagr
am\n    participant C as Flutter App\n    participant API as MatchingController\
n    participant S as MatchingService\n    participant DB as MySQL\n    particip
ant R as Redis\n\n    C->>API: GET /matching/recommendations\n    API->>S: getRe
commendations(userId, location, filters)\n    S->>R: get candidate pool\n    alt
cache miss\n        S->>DB: query candidates (Haversine + filters)\n        DB--
>>S: user list\n        S->>R: cache candidate pool (TTL 5min)\n    end\n    S--
>>API: sorted cards\n    API-->>C: 200 OK\n```\n\n### 滑动与匹配\n\n```mermaid\n
sequenceDiagram\n    participant C as Flutter App\n    participant API as Matchi
ngController\n    participant S as MatchingService\n    participant DB as MySQL\
n    participant WS as Socket.io\n\n    C->>API: POST /matching/actions (target_
id, action=like)\n    API->>S: recordAction(userId, targetId, action)\n    S->>D
B: insert match_actions\n    S->>DB: checkMutualLike(targetId, userId)\n    alt 
mutual like\n        S->>DB: create match + conversation\n        S->>WS: emit m
atch:created to both users\n    end\n    S-->>API: result\n    API-->>C: 200 OK\
n```\n\n## Flutter 架构\n\n### BLoC / Event / State\n\n#### MatchingBloc（首页推
荐 + 滑动）\n\n```dart\n// matching_bloc.dart\nclass MatchingBloc extends Bloc<M
atchingEvent, MatchingState> { ... }\n\n// matching_event.dart\nabstract class M
atchingEvent {}\nclass RecommendationsRequested extends MatchingEvent {\n  final
String mode; // 'nearby' | 'city' | 'nationwide'\n}\nclass SwipeActionSubmitted 
extends MatchingEvent {\n  final String targetId;\n  final SwipeAction action; /
/ like | pass\n}\nclass MatchModalDismissed extends MatchingEvent {}\n\n// match
ing_state.dart\nabstract class MatchingState {}\nclass MatchingInitial extends M
atchingState {}\nclass MatchingLoadInProgress extends MatchingState {}\nclass Ma
tchingLoadSuccess extends MatchingState {\n  final List<RecommendationCard> card
s;\n  final String mode;\n}\nclass MatchingLoadEmpty extends MatchingState {\n  
final String mode;\n}\nclass MatchingSwipeInProgress extends MatchingState {\n  
final List<RecommendationCard> cards;\n  final String targetId;\n  final SwipeAc
tion action;\n}\nclass MatchingMatchCreated extends MatchingState {\n  final Mat
chSummary match; // 用于弹窗展示\n}\nclass MatchingFailure extends MatchingState
{\n  final String message;\n}\n```\n\n#### MatchListCubit（匹配列表）\n\n```dart
\n// match_list_cubit.dart\nclass MatchListCubit extends Cubit<MatchListState> {
\n  Future<void> fetchMatches({String? cursor}) async { ... }\n}\n\n// match_lis
t_state.dart\nabstract class MatchListState {}\nclass MatchListInitial extends M
atchListState {}\nclass MatchListLoadInProgress extends MatchListState {}\nclass
MatchListLoadSuccess extends MatchListState {\n  final List<MatchItem> matches;\
n  final bool hasMore;\n  final String? nextCursor;\n}\nclass MatchListLoadFailu
re extends MatchListState {\n  final String message;\n}\n```\n\n### 组件清单\n\n
| 层级 | 组件名 | 文件路径 | 说明 |\n|------|--------|----------|------|\n| atom
| `SwActionButton` | `packages/design-system/lib/src/atoms/sw_action_button.dart
` | 圆形操作按钮（Pass/Like 两种变体） |\n| molecule | `SwipeCard` | `packages/d
esign-system/lib/src/molecules/swipe_card.dart` | 可拖动/可点击的推荐用户卡片 |\
n| organism | `SwipeCardStack` | `packages/design-system/lib/src/organisms/swipe
